.TH wsp-repo-add 1  "add " 
.SH NAME
add \- Add repos to current workspace
.SH SYNOPSIS
\fBadd\fR [\fB\-g\fR|\fB\-\-group\fR] [\fB\-h\fR|\fB\-\-help\fR] [\fIrepos\fR] 
.SH DESCRIPTION
Add repos to current workspace
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-g\fR, \fB\-\-group\fR
Add repos from a group
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
Print help
.TP
[\fIrepos\fR]

